---
title: Double Creamy Bacon Spaghetti with Lemon & Garlic Pangrattato
description: Calling all pasta lovers there’s a quick and easy hot dish ready for you to cook and eat! Whip it up in no time at all
with a zesty pangrattato and creamy sauce packed with the all-star favourites, bacon and Parmesan. Serve with a
fresh garden salad for a splash of vibrant (and yummy) green and you have a dish ready for any lover of pasta.
